{
  "text": "Third, while ChatGPT offers large amounts of information at lightning speed, students pointed out AI's lack of higher-order thinking as reflected by the top 3 levels of Bloom's taxonomy: (1) analysis (the ability to deconstruction information, and/or examine it from differing perspectives), (2) evaluation (the ability to form educated judgments and form relevant critiques) and (3) creation (the ability to present learned information in new and unique ways) (Anderson & Krathwohl, 2001) which posed a significant challenge.",
  "mask": "(Anderson & Krathwohl, 2001)",
